      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>党内元老退却，日本领导人之争悬而未决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/japan-s-leadership-race-is-wide-open-as-party-elders-retreat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本执政党领袖竞选于周四拉开帷幕，由于党内元老的控制力减弱，创纪录数量的候选人可以参与公开竞选，以带领国家度过关键的过渡期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/japan-s-leadership-race-is-wide-open-as-party-elders-retreat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 00:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称英国 NHS 资金缺口达 370 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/england-s-nhs-broken-by-37-billion-investment-gap-ara-darzi-s-report-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份报告指出，英格兰国民健康服务体系 (NHS) 因缺乏资金而陷入瘫痪已逾 10 年，该报告揭示了新任首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 在重建这个根植于国民精神的组织时所面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/england-s-nhs-broken-by-37-billion-investment-gap-ara-darzi-s-report-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济学家称泰国新总理的改革议程缺乏具体内容</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/new-thai-pm-s-reform-blueprint-lacks-specifics-economists-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国新任总理制定了应对最紧迫问题的路线图，包括接近创纪录的家庭债务、低迷的经济增长和老龄化社会。但经济学家认为，该计划缺乏确保在规定时间内取得成果的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/new-thai-pm-s-reform-blueprint-lacks-specifics-economists-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以下是日本下一任领导人的九位候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[9 月 27 日，日本执政党自民党将举行领导人选举，将有创纪录的 9 名候选人参选。由于自民党在议会中占据主导地位，此次选举几乎肯定会产生日本下一任首相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 02:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
